name: Fill Up Yum Yum's Tum Tum
name_original: Fill Up Yum Yum's Tum Tum
description:
A Yum Yum has crashed down to Earth! Dr. Poopyman had originally been tasked with taking care of it, however due to a work related accident, the mantle has been passed on.

Now it is up to you, Dr. Winkleboozybottom, to save this poor creature from near certain starvation! 

Special Thanks to all those involved!
